reviewText: Great movies. Of course though, one would wish it was longer.
Excellent film. Jon Proudstar was great!
Lots of emotion packed into a short film! The lead actors gave really moving performances and Boo Boo Stewart is so good! He is well on his way proving he is a serious and diverse actor!
Loved the movie wished it would have been longer to fill in gaps in the story line though! For being a short film, my opinion is it was awesome.
